              class="rounded h-60 w-50 pb-3 mx-auto d-block"
            />
            <a href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/donate" class="btn btn-block btn-sm btn-info" role="button">Donate!</a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>
              <strong>The World Health Organization</strong> Solidarity Response
              Fund is an international effort to combat the drastic effects of
              the COVID-19. They provide funding to various organizations
              worldwide in an effort to prevent the spread of the disease while
              simultaneously improving the magnitude and efficiency of testing
              and providing an immediate response to adverse situations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!--Sixth Donation Link-->
